<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Share Your Review</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; margin: 0; padding: 20px; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #f59e0b; padding: 28px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; }
    .stars { font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 4px; }
    .body { padding: 40px; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.6; text-align: center; }
    .btn { display: inline-block; background: #f59e0b; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .footer { padding: 24px 40px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; text-align: center; }
    .footer p { color: #999; font-size: 12px; margin: 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
      <h1>How was {{eventTitle}}?</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <p>Thank you for attending <strong>{{eventTitle}}</strong>! We'd love to hear about your experience.</p>
      <p>Your feedback helps us improve future events and helps other attendees make informed decisions.</p>
      <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="btn">Leave a Review</a>
      <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #aaa;">It only takes 2 minutes!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Assembl. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
